<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Ok here is the deal. I have found that with sow and my weighted axe I can do a ton of damage on a hill giant in rathe mtns when I pull back to group. I am nearly level 40 and this is my question, do you think this "warrior kiting" will work as a solo tactic. The plan is simple, smash with the axe (I hit for in the 200's regularly and sometimes in the 300's and 400's numbers this high are rare though) and run away with sow untill I get my next attack and then stop and smash again.<p>

Whaddya think?<p>

Lemme know and please no spamming on this sucks and I could kill you in a duel and so on. If you don't believe that I can do this kind of damage with the axe then post your email address here and I will send you one of the MANY screen shots that I have.<p>

Thx in advance<p>

Krallek, Drunken Ogre Warrior of Brell Serillis<br>
