<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Nope, not relying on crits or god forbid crips at all. I AM however, relying on double attacks which happen often. I usually get a double attack in 2 out of every 3 swings (2 out of 4 at worst). With each attack in the area of 100 damage, thats roughly 200 damage per swing. I do miss probably 1 out of every 3 swings for sure, especially with mobs with good ac like a HG. <p>

At any rate, I do understand the need to group at higher levels and have many "friends" at or around my own level. This technique would be for money making only and not for any great exp gains. The hgs are capable of dropping as much as 40 plats per mob and that will more than pay for the sow potions used. <p>

So far though, I am kinda dissapointed in the posts here. I did ask for posts that were on topic and not various spams on peeps opinions whether I should be grouping or do I have god weapons and such. Come on folks, there has to be someone out there who has tried this!<p>

